26
00:01:13.320 --> 00:01:16.470
<v ->All right, the first one I wanna answer is the,</v>

27
00:01:16.470 --> 00:01:19.200
do the GLP show sustained weight loss

28
00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:21.000
or are they also subject

29
00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.220
