universities, almost all universities have

99
00:04:25.650 --> 00:04:28.263
behavioral health programs for weight loss.

100
00:04:29.250 --> 00:04:30.903
Look in your community.

101
00:04:31.853 --> 00:04:36.853
And the CDC has a family healthy weight program

102
00:04:37.500 --> 00:04:39.540
that will at least get you started.

103
00:04:39.540 --> 00:04:42.570
But there are resources all over the place for these.

104
00:04:42.570 --> 00:04:43.980
<v ->And definitely look online.</v>

105
00:04:43.980 --> 00:04:45.480
There are lots of now support groups

106
00:04:45.480 --> 00:04:48.450
that are available online for individuals

107
00:04:48.450 --> 00:04:50.550
that will be exceedingly helpful to families

108
00:04:50.550 --> 00:04:52.950
who are dealing with this chronic issue.

