160
00:07:28.530 --> 00:07:31.830
So does it make sense that I might consider that?

161
00:07:31.830 --> 00:07:33.450
Sure, it makes sense.

162
00:07:33.450 --> 00:07:36.450
I mean, if I have alternate uses

163
00:07:36.450 --> 00:07:39.690
for putting them on the venlafaxine

164
00:07:39.690 --> 00:07:43.233
as opposed to just managing the low back pain,

165
00:07:44.375 --> 00:07:45.600
then I might consider that

166
00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:48.313
if they don't tolerate the duloxetine.

167
00:07:48.313 --> 00:07:50.220
I don't know the answer to it.

168
00:07:50.220 --> 00:07:54.270
We haven't studied it to give you the answer yet.

169
00:07:54.270 --> 00:07:58.260
And then the last question I'll hit here is I use ibuprofen

170
00:07:58.260 --> 00:08:01.960
in combination with acetaminophen to treat pain

171
00:08:02.820 --> 00:08:05.820
because the combination seems to work well.

172
00:08:05.820 --> 00:08:08.853
So the answer, I agree.

173
00:08:09.930 --> 00:08:10.763
Okay.

174
00:08:13.350 --> 00:08:16.440
This is multimodal pain therapy

175
00:08:16.440 --> 00:08:18.660
and we use multimodal pain therapy

176
00:08:18.660 --> 00:08:21.510
in acute and chronic pain.

177
00:08:21.510 --> 00:08:23.430
And so it works,

178
00:08:23.430 --> 00:08:25.860
but when I put them head to head,

179
00:08:25.860 --> 00:08:28.080
acetaminophen and ibuprofen,

180
00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:31.860
acetaminophen gives no relief in acute low back pain

181
00:08:31.860 --> 00:08:36.150
and ibuprofen gives significant relief in low back pain.

182
00:08:36.150 --> 00:08:39.750
So when I combine them together,

183
00:08:39.750 --> 00:08:42.900
is it the ibuprofen or the non-steroidal

184
00:08:42.900 --> 00:08:45.120
that's really providing all the analgesia

185
00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:46.740
and not the acetaminophen?

186
00:08:46.740 --> 00:08:47.850
I don't know.

187
00:08:47.850 --> 00:08:49.860
Is it really problematic?

188
00:08:49.860 --> 00:08:52.830
No, it's not really problematic to put them together

189
00:08:52.830 --> 00:08:55.020
because again, that's the basis

190
00:08:55.020 --> 00:08:57.603
of multimodal analgesic therapy.

