00:23:39.240 --> 00:23:41.190
I don't like that term.

520
00:23:41.190 --> 00:23:46.190
And a better term is really optimization for surgery.

521
00:23:46.500 --> 00:23:49.920
And so if you are uncomfortable putting cleared for surgery,

522
00:23:49.920 --> 00:23:52.710
write that the patient is optimized for surgery.

523
00:23:52.710 --> 00:23:55.770
<v ->I actually will cross out the clear piece</v>

524
00:23:55.770 --> 00:23:57.870
and I put risk stratification

525
00:23:57.870 --> 00:23:59.970
and that they're optimized for surgery.

526
00:23:59.970 --> 00:24:02.190
I mean, that's what you can say about it.

527
00:24:02.190 --> 00:24:03.180
Oh, you have one more?

