00:24:16.470 --> 00:24:17.760
'cause they're easier,

536
00:24:17.760 --> 00:24:19.110
especially the ones that have been around a while,

537
00:24:19.110 --> 00:24:21.870
oral bisphosphonates and they're cheaper.

538
00:24:21.870 --> 00:24:25.320
And then, to answer a good question, is it,

