00:24:49.853 --> 00:24:50.970
than they thought they were going to,

551
00:24:50.970 --> 00:24:52.620
it's reasonable to get a DXA scan.

552
00:24:52.620 --> 00:24:53.910
So there's really no good guideline.

553
00:24:53.910 --> 00:24:56.160
I'd be shocked if it showed up on your test

554
00:24:56.160 --> 00:24:59.880
and I'll answer all the rest of them online.

