00:24:59.880 --> 00:25:01.163
<v Dr. Weismiller>Dr. Garry.</v>

556
00:25:02.250 --> 00:25:05.280
<v ->How does Little League elbow differ from golfer's elbow?</v>

557
00:25:05.280 --> 00:25:06.840
You're at the right location,

558
00:25:06.840 --> 00:25:10.470
but remember, it's the apophysis versus the tendon.

559
00:25:10.470 --> 00:25:13.560
Little League elbow is an apophysitis.

560
00:25:13.560 --> 00:25:14.967
It's not affecting the tendon,

561
00:25:14.967 --> 00:25:17.580
the tendon's pulling the two pieces

562
00:25:17.580 --> 00:25:19.650
of bone away from each other.

563
00:25:19.650 --> 00:25:23.847
And it's that apophysis that is the pathology.

564
00:25:25.380 --> 00:25:28.860
Whereas in golfer's elbow,

565
00:25:28.860 --> 00:25:32.310
it's actually the tendon that is the pathology

566
00:25:32.310 --> 00:25:35.250
that has some chronic degenerative change in it.

567
00:25:35.250 --> 00:25:39.323
And then question about why the sed rate and CRP,

568
00:25:39.323 --> 00:25:42.060
wouldn't the CRP be good enough?

569
00:25:42.060 --> 00:25:44.580
Look, I'm just giving, (chuckles)

570
00:25:44.580 --> 00:25:48.360
I'm giving you the data that the board likes.

571
00:25:48.360 --> 00:25:51.840
In actuality, there have been, there was a follow-up study

572
00:25:51.840 --> 00:25:55.500
that looked just at CRP and weight bearing status.

573
00:25:55.500 --> 00:26:00.180
And if my CRP is normal and I'm weight bearing,

574
00:26:00.180 --> 00:26:03.870
the likelihood of a septic hip is less than 1%.

575
00:26:03.870 --> 00:26:07.620
So I like that data markedly better,

576
00:26:07.620 --> 00:26:10.500
but this is the data that you're gonna be asked about.

577
00:26:10.500 --> 00:26:14.163
So that's why I'm giving you that piece.

578
00:26:16.740 --> 00:26:20.853
I'm just trying to toggle back to the other session.

579
00:26:25.860 --> 00:26:28.770
<v ->While he's doing that, I'll just say stop warfarin</v>

580
00:26:28.770 --> 00:26:33.420
five days prior to surgery, stop aspirin and clopidogrel,

581
00:26:33.420 --> 00:26:35.400
if you're stopping them separately,

582
00:26:35.400 --> 00:26:37.503
those are both five to seven days.

583
00:26:42.303 --> 00:26:47.220
<v ->So for sports related concussion, do you really,</v>

584
00:26:47.220 --> 00:26:50.550
what's the limitation on activity?

585
00:26:50.550 --> 00:26:54.330
24 to 48 hours of no activity

586
00:26:54.330 --> 00:26:56.790
and limit all their cognitive stuff,

587
00:26:56.790 --> 00:27:01.140
no TV, no computer use, no telephone, screen use,

588
00:27:01.140 --> 00:27:04.590
limit all that for 24 to 48 hours.

589
00:27:04.590 --> 00:27:06.630
How do I decide?

590
00:27:06.630 --> 00:27:09.900
It depends, however it works.

591
00:27:09.900 --> 00:27:12.210
You can say 24, you can say 48.

592
00:27:12.210 --> 00:27:14.010
It's really not any different.

593
00:27:14.010 --> 00:27:15.900
At that point in time,

594
00:27:15.900 --> 00:27:19.200
tell them I want you to start participating

595
00:27:19.200 --> 00:27:21.480
in some kind of light activity

596
00:27:21.480 --> 00:27:25.470
that doesn't make your symptoms worse, okay?

597
00:27:25.470 --> 00:27:27.750
So 24 to 48 hours rest

598
00:27:27.750 --> 00:27:31.470
and then they start light activity at that point in time

599
00:27:31.470 --> 00:27:35.190
to a threshold that doesn't make their symptoms worse.

600
00:27:35.190 --> 00:27:38.703
And then should there be imaging, it's great question,

601
00:27:39.627 --> 00:27:42.090
should be there imaging if I have loss subconsciousness

602
00:27:42.090 --> 00:27:44.463
with a sports related concussion?

603
00:27:45.570 --> 00:27:47.103
The answer is,

604
00:27:48.743 --> 00:27:51.600
this is the technical answer.

605
00:27:51.600 --> 00:27:54.990
If I don't have focal neurologic signs or symptoms

606
00:27:54.990 --> 00:27:56.640
when I awaken,

607
00:27:56.640 --> 00:27:58.893
then no, there should be no imaging.

608
00:28:00.720 --> 00:28:02.610
What would most of us do?

609
00:28:02.610 --> 00:28:05.430
Most of us would probably image in that case.

610
00:28:05.430 --> 00:28:07.590
Thankfully, you don't have loss subconsciousness

611
00:28:07.590 --> 00:28:09.810
with sports related concussion very often.

612
00:28:09.810 --> 00:28:12.630
And it typically occurs in the second, third,

613
00:28:12.630 --> 00:28:15.510
or fourth concussion, not in the first one.

614
00:28:15.510 --> 00:28:16.860
<v ->So Russell, please go ahead.</v>

615
00:28:16.860 --> 00:28:17.700
Thank you, sir.

