00:28:39.660 --> 00:28:42.840
and the side effects are low,

624
00:28:42.840 --> 00:28:46.380
it is preventing them from having cardiovascular events.

625
00:28:46.380 --> 00:28:49.940
If anything, we're probably undertreating with statins.

626
00:28:49.940 --> 00:28:52.350
If you look at people for secondary prevention,

