00:30:30.150 --> 00:30:32.790
<v ->Okay, just to, I just wanna emphasize here though.</v>

664
00:30:32.790 --> 00:30:37.790
On the exam, they're gonna ask you 55 to 69 every other year

665
00:30:38.940 --> 00:30:40.380
if you're going to do it,

666
00:30:40.380 --> 00:30:41.910
if you're gonna do it, okay.

667
00:30:41.910 --> 00:30:46.530
Don't get, don't be adding things to the question, okay?

