00:34:05.040 --> 00:34:08.220
Can hydroxychloroquine be used as a first line agent?

748
00:34:08.220 --> 00:34:09.300
I think this is a good question

749
00:34:09.300 --> 00:34:12.990
because you always want to use as a non-biologic agent,

750
00:34:12.990 --> 00:34:16.260
you always want to use your methotrexate first.

751
00:34:16.260 --> 00:34:18.810
If methotrexate is not getting the job done,

752
00:34:18.810 --> 00:34:22.560
then add second hydroxychloroquine.

