00:34:25.230 --> 00:34:27.540
it's okay to start with hydroxychloroquine,

755
00:34:27.540 --> 00:34:29.430
but methotrexate, your number one,

756
00:34:29.430 --> 00:34:31.560
hydroxychloroquine will be your number two,

