1289
00:57:31.860 --> 00:57:35.640
Do babies of iron deficient mothers need iron

1290
00:57:35.640 --> 00:57:37.530
sooner than four months?

1291
00:57:37.530 --> 00:57:38.520
The answer is no,

1292
00:57:38.520 --> 00:57:40.860
because babies are very efficient little parasites.

1293
00:57:40.860 --> 00:57:42.450
They will suck up all the iron they need

1294
00:57:42.450 --> 00:57:44.100
into their bodies before they're born.

1295
00:57:44.100 --> 00:57:46.850
So they're born with about four months worth of stores.

