1312
00:58:19.410 --> 00:58:20.400
So it depends on the diet.

1313
00:58:20.400 --> 00:58:21.433
Typically, around nine to 12 months

1314
00:58:21.433 --> 00:58:22.980
when they're eating table foods,

1315
00:58:22.980 --> 00:58:26.130
as long as the family's eating food with iron in it.

1316
00:58:26.130 --> 00:58:28.230
Youngest age, you start juice for constipation,

1317
00:58:28.230 --> 00:58:29.850
usually about four to six months

1318
00:58:29.850 --> 00:58:31.740
about the time you introduce food.

1319
00:58:31.740 --> 00:58:34.170
For breastfeeding moms is 6,400 international units

1320
00:58:34.170 --> 00:58:35.433
of vitamin D daily.

1321
00:58:36.270 --> 00:58:38.100
That's just what the research has shown.

1322
00:58:38.100 --> 00:58:42.153
My mom usually take a 5 to 10,000 capsule per day.

1323
00:58:44.100 --> 00:58:45.750
