1335
00:59:14.400 --> 00:59:16.500
I would highly recommend that you,

1336
00:59:16.500 --> 00:59:18.630
rather than trying to plot it out on a chart by yourself,

1337
00:59:18.630 --> 00:59:21.153
use one of the many great tools out there.

1338
00:59:22.912 --> 00:59:24.840
Is there a difference in colic rates between breastfed

1339
