1465
01:04:25.500 --> 01:04:27.780
If you hear a lot of snoring, stopping breathing.

1466
01:04:27.780 --> 01:04:29.820
Also, if they have hypertension and they're obese,

1467
01:04:29.820 --> 01:04:32.460
you probably wanna screen for obstructive sleep apnea.

1468
01:04:32.460 --> 01:04:33.870
Multivitamins.

1469
01:04:33.870 --> 01:04:36.120
Some multivitamins also have recommended folic acid,

1470
01:04:36.120 --> 01:04:37.230
although they're not prenatal.

1471
01:04:37.230 --> 01:04:38.610
Yes, you can do that.

1472
01:04:38.610 --> 01:04:42.270
Any multivitamin that's got folic acid in it is fine.

1473
01:04:42.270 --> 01:04:45.150
Winter routinely screen for anemia.

1474
01:04:45.150 --> 01:04:47.670
So the American Academy of Pediatrics recommends

1475
01:04:47.670 --> 01:04:49.110
between six and 12 months.

1476
01:04:49.110 --> 01:04:50.160
So if you're going to screen,

1477
01:04:50.160 --> 01:04:51.990
that's the time that you're gonna screen for it.

1478
01:04:51.990 --> 01:04:53.490
When do you screen for lipids?

