01:05:32.430 --> 01:05:33.263
or there's a problem

1495
01:05:33.263 --> 01:05:35.040
'cause now you're doing diagnosis,

1496
01:05:35.040 --> 01:05:37.640
but you do not do any screening under the age of 21.

